doctype html
head
  meta(charset='UTF-8')
  meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge')
  meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  title Risk1
  link(rel='stylesheet' href='../static/Style.css')
  script(src='../static/JavaScript.js' defer='')
div
  div
    br
    h1    Please assess the risk level of the event described below 
    br
  div
    p#RiskDescription
      | At 10 am, you received an email from someone with the same name as your credit card company,
      br
      | informing you that a specific detailes in your account is missing and providing instructions on how to send it back to them. 
      br
      | The instructions state to include the credit card number, the three-digit code on the back of the card, as well as your name and ID card.
  br
  form(action='/insertClick' method='POST')
    input(type='hidden' name='redirect_url' value='/Detalis') 
    input(type='hidden' name='RiskID' value='Risk10-Group2')
    .slidecontainer
    label(for='Riskrate') 0 - No Risk 
    input#myRange(type='range' name='Riskrate' class='riskSlider' min='0' max='100' step='1' oninput="document.getElementById('sliderValue').innerHTML = this.value; enableSubmit()")
    label(for='myRange') 100 - Very High Risk
    p#sliderValue 50
    div
    button(type='submit' id='submitRisk' disabled) Submit
